description: A standalone Dart script demonstrating note serialization and deserialization outside of a Flutter environment. It creates a Note object, encodes it to a JSON string, decodes it back to a Note object, and prints a summary to stdout.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Data model representing a note, including title, content, pinned status, creation and update timestamps, and possibly color.

methods.name: main
methods.description: Entry point of the script that creates, serializes, deserializes, and prints a Note object.
